textBox.richText: A new journal article resulting from a joint work between the team and the University Autonoma de Madrid (UAM) on face, iris and fingerprint anti-spoofing has been accepted for publication to Transactions on Image Processing: J. Galbally, S. Marcel, and J. Fierrez. Image quality assessment for fake biometric detection: Application to iris, fingerprint and face recognition.  IEEE Transactions on Image Processing, 2013. [IEEEXplore]
New journal article in Transactions on Image Processing
